{
 "name": "RPlog_Painfully_Stubborn",
 "title": "Painfully Stubborn",
 "summary": "In the cleared grounds before the main house at Karrde's base on Myrkr, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios and the dark adept Simon Sezirok share a charged, stubborn encounter. The two strong-willed Force users probe and resist one another, each unwilling to give ground in their tangled relationship. As dusk approaches and the dangers of Myrkr's forest stir, Simon urges them both to safety and offers to share a meal, and Jessalyn takes him by the arm, turning the conversation toward Karrde and their next move. The scene captures the prickly, intimate dynamic between the two.",
